  "detailed_description": "<strong>After a strange virus spreads across an Arctic Island, you are left all alone.</strong><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1795180/extras/4dd4833ab3fb5053d3b605d0e9eb4314.poster.avif?t=1693986859\" width=480 height=190 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1795180/extras/4dd4833ab3fb5053d3b605d0e9eb4314.webm?t=1693986859\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1795180/extras/4dd4833ab3fb5053d3b605d0e9eb4314.mp4?t=1693986859\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>Your mission is to survive for as many days as you can.</strong><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1795180/extras/8ad5ce1691363d592a81dc86c05afa21.poster.avif?t=1693986859\" width=480 height=146 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1795180/extras/8ad5ce1691363d592a81dc86c05afa21.webm?t=1693986859\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1795180/extras/8ad5ce1691363d592a81dc86c05afa21.mp4?t=1693986859\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>Scavenge for food, drink, medical supplies, weapons, ammunition, clothes and fuel.</strong><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1795180/extras/d34d0da95ab27ca2b5154a79752c2723.poster.avif?t=1693986859\" width=480 height=146 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1795180/extras/d34d0da95ab27ca2b5154a79752c2723.webm?t=1693986859\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1795180/extras/d34d0da95ab27ca2b5154a79752c2723.mp4?t=1693986859\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>Find shelters, vehicles and other interesting locations to help you survive.</strong><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1795180/extras/8b4fafae48f5a333be27b28cf4c86f2d.poster.avif?t=1693986859\" width=480 height=146 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1795180/extras/8b4fafae48f5a333be27b28cf4c86f2d.webm?t=1693986859\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1795180/extras/8b4fafae48f5a333be27b28cf4c86f2d.mp4?t=1693986859\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Ice Station Z was developed by Wobbly Tooth using the Unreal Engine® and uses player hosted servers. <br>A gamepad is recommended but it does support keyboard & mouse as well.<br><br>Wobbly Tooth is a solo indie developer. For bugs and suggestions contact<br><a href=\"mailto:info@wobbly-tooth.com\">info@wobbly-tooth.com</a>",
